# volume settings, using common keycodes
# if these don't work, use xev to find out your real keycodes
Mod1 112 :Exec amixer sset Master 10%+ # Alt+PageUp
Mod1 117 :Exec amixer sset Master 10%- # Alt+PageDown
Mod1 115 :Exec amixer sset Master,0 toggle # Alt+End

